Package com.randallscharpf.java.jmorsecoding.base.symbolsets

Translations from written symbols to Morse Code units.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MorseSymbolSet
    A translator from written characters and prosigns to dashes and dots.
    SymbolSetBase.MorseSymbol
    A character or prosign that can be played as Morse Code.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExtendedInternationalSymbolSet
    A symbol set that attempts to be able to convert any valid Unicode string to the Morse code sequence that corresponds to that string according to general consensus.
    InternationalSymbolSet
    A symbol set that follows the conventions established by ITU-R 2009 standards.
    SymbolSetBase
    A concrete implementation of a MorseSymbolSet implemented using an enum.
    SymbolSetBase.CharOrProsign
    Either a character or a prosign.

Package com.randallscharpf.java.jmorsecoding.base.symbolsets Description

Translations from written symbols to Morse Code units. Provides interfaces and implementations for conversion from characters and prosigns to dots, dashes, and spaces between them.
Since:
1.0
